-absent from the FIFA Best Awards at the La Scala Opera house in Milan, on Tuesday took to Instagram to express his feelings in philosophical terms. Ronaldo missed out as Lionel Messi was named FIFA Best Player of the Year for the sixth time on Monday. The Juventus… September 24, 2019 In "News" Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo decided against travelling to London for FIFA’s The Best award ceremony last night. September 25, 2018 In "Sports" Liverpool centre-back Virgil van Dijk is on the shortlist to add FIFA's best player award to his UEFA Men's Player of the Year honour. September 2, 2019 In "News"